Useful files for vscode users  
extensions.json recommends extensions  

One may use the launch.json as taken from  
https://root.cern/blog/root-on-vscode/  

And one may view root files directly in vscode
https://root.cern/blog/vscode-extension-announcement/

If you would like to SetEnv, cmake .., make, runMC.C check tasks.json
On vscode you may start this task chain with CTRL+SHIFT+B
